# ToolbarDivider Component Rule

The [ToolbarDivider.vue](mdc:src/components/ui/ToolbarDivider.vue) component follows shadcn-vue conventions:

- Single File Component (SFC) in `src/components/ui`.
- Used for visually separating groups of toolbar actions.
- Accepts `horizontal` prop to control orientation (default: vertical divider).
- Uses Tailwind CSS for styling and utility classes.

For toolbar best practices, see the [shadcn-vue Toolbar documentation](https://www.shadcn-vue.com/docs/components/toolbar) as a reference.
